<p>Governor Hope Uzodinma of the All Progressives Congress has won the governorship election in Orlu Local Government, He scored&nbsp;37,614&nbsp;votes, to defeat his&nbsp;closest rival,&nbsp; the candidate of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP),&nbsp;&nbsp;Sam Anyanwu, who scored&nbsp;3,690&nbsp;votes.</p>



<p>The results announced at the Independent National Electoral Commission (INEC) State Collation Centre in Owerri, showed that the candidate&nbsp;of the Labour Party, Athan Achonu, scored&nbsp;2,424&nbsp;votes.</p>



